# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in real values. Never commit `.env.local`.
#
# PRODUCTION (Vercel): set every var below in the *frontend* Vercel project's Settings ->
# Environment Variables (scope: Production). `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` vars are inlined into the
# client bundle at build time, so a change requires a redeploy. Set NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL to
# the deployed *backend* origin, and add that same frontend origin to the backend's
# CORS_ORIGINS. Full runbook: docs/DEPLOYMENT.md.
#
# Publishable + secret keys come from the SAME Clerk application as the backend's
# CLERK_JWKS_URL/CLERK_ISSUER (backend/.env) — Configure > API Keys in the Clerk
# dashboard. These are different key *types* from the backend's (frontend needs the
# publishable/secret pair to run Clerk's sign-in UI; the backend only verifies tokens
# via JWKS), but both come from the same app.
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...

# The backend API's base URL (see backend/app/core/config.py's cors_origins — this
# frontend's origin must be in that list for requests here to not get blocked by CORS).
# PROD (Vercel): the deployed backend origin, e.g. https://studymate-api.vercel.app or a
# custom domain like https://api.yourdomain.com.
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000

# --- Observability (Sentry + PostHog) — both optional, both fully env-gated ---
# Unset = off, everywhere (src/instrumentation-client.ts, src/instrumentation.ts,
# app/providers.tsx) — never a crash, same convention as every other optional key in
# this project. A Sentry DSN is not a secret (it already ships in this same bundle),
# so one NEXT_PUBLIC_ var covers client, server, and edge — see instrumentation.ts.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SENTRY_DSN=https://...@....ingest.us.sentry.io/...

# From your PostHog project's settings. NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST must be the API host
# (e.g. https://us.i.posthog.com or https://eu.i.posthog.com for EU-hosted projects,
# or your self-hosted URL) — NOT a dashboard/session-replay page URL; defaults to the
# US cloud host if unset.
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_...
NEXT_PUBLIC_POSTHOG_HOST=https://us.i.posthog.com
